# Security Improvements Implemented

- Used lightweight Alpine base image
- Removed unnecessary packages
- Used non-root container user
- Implemented IAM least privilege access
- Configured secure networking
- Performed vulnerability scanning before deployment

---

# Results

| Task | Status |
|---|---|
| Docker Containerization | Completed |
| Trivy Vulnerability Scanning | Completed |
| ECS Fargate Deployment | Completed |
| Public Access Configuration | Completed |
| CloudWatch Monitoring | Completed |
| Security Hardening | Completed |

---

# Challenges Faced

| Challenge | Solution |
|---|---|
| IAM Permission Errors | Updated IAM Policies |
| ECS Execution Role Issues | Created ECS Role Manually |
| Public IP Access Issues | Enabled Auto Assign Public IP |
| Docker Port Mapping Problems | Fixed Task Definition Ports |

